  "body": "Some notes about `update_validator_registry`:\r\n\r\n* there's a `return` at the end that shouldn't be there\r\n* `latest_penalized_exit_balances` needs to be accessed through `state.latest_penalized_exit_balances`\r\n* `state.latest_penalized_exit_balances` is initialized to empty list never grown, so accesses will be invalid\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/a2422de686b026c9a85549331c2a3181fa369ccc/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#validator-registry\r\n",
